content: जू {c1c} <ab>U.</ab> {c9c} <ab>P.</ab> (जवति-ते, जुनाति) {@--1@} To press or hurry on, move on quickly. {@--2@} To impel quickly, urge or drive on. {@--3@} To excite, animate, inspire.

जूः {%<ab>f.</ab>%} {@--1@} Speed. {@--2@} Atmosphere. {@--3@} A female demon. {@--4@} An epithet of Sarasvatī. {@--5@} Going speedily, quick motion. {@--6@} A mark on the forehead of horses and oxen.
